1 WHEREAS, Bob's philanthropic endeavors have inspired his descendants to follow
2 a similarly civic-minded and charitable path; their work has benefitted many institutions in
3 New Orleans, including the National World War II Museum, Tulane University, City Park,
4 and numerous Catholic charities; and
5 WHEREAS, Robert E. "Bob" Smith Lupo is most deserving of the highest
6 recognition for his outstanding dedication to Lakeview and the city of New Orleans.
7 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
8 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Robert E. "Bob" Smith Lupo for his service
9 to Lakeview and the city of New Orleans and does hereby encourage citizens to follow his
10 example of civic-minded service and philanthropic work.
